OL,6,FA DJ who filmed himself urinating on a
OL,7,Fcancer patient in a social club before
OL,8,Fposting the video online has been
OL,9,Fjailed for 14 weeks.
OL,11,FLeigh Brookfield, 40, previously
OL,12,Fadmitted assaulting Peter Barton at
OL,13,FLlanelli Tennis and Squash Club in the
OL,14,Ftown on December 26 last year.
OL,16,FLlanelli Magistrates' Court heard
OL,17,FBrookfield, of Dan Y Lan in Llanelli,
OL,18,Fhad been standing next to Mr Barton at
OL,19,Fthe urinals of the club when the
OL,20,Fincident took place.
