OL,6,FMr Barton told Brookfield about his
OL,7,Fcancer diagnosis, with the DJ then
OL,8,Furinating on the back of his trousers.
OL,10,FBrookfield later posted a video of
OL,11,Fwhat happened to social media platform
OL,12,FSnapchat.
OL,14,FIn a victim personal statement read to
OL,15,Fthe court, Mr Barton said: "When I saw
OL,16,Fthis video I actually cried.
OL,18,F"I couldn't believe someone would do
OL,19,Fthat to another person.
