OL,6,F"I was breathless and my blood
OL,7,Fpressure was through the roof.
OL,9,F"I just feel that his actions were
OL,10,Fabsolutely disgusting."
OL,12,FMr Barton described the video as
OL,13,F"extremely upsetting" and said he felt
OL,14,Fconcerned that people might recognise
OL,15,Fhim because of it.
OL,17,FThe court heard Brookfield has
OL,18,Fprevious convictions for alcohol-
OL,19,Frelated offences.
