OL,6,F"Most people would have responded with
OL,7,Fkind words of sympathy," Judge Layton
OL,8,Ftold him.
OL,10,F"Your response was to urinate on the
OL,11,Fback of his clothing which you filmed."
OL,13,FHe went on to call it an assault on a
OL,14,Fvulnerable victim who was unaware at
OL,15,Fthe time. He added that Mr Barton was
OL,16,Funaware of what happened until he saw
OL,17,Fthe video.
