OL,6,FJudge Layton imposed a 14-week prison
OL,7,Fsentence, of which Brookfield will
OL,8,Fserve half before being released, and
OL,9,Fordered him to pay #500 compensation,
OL,10,Fa #154 surcharge and #85 in costs.
OL,12,FIn a statement posted on Facebook
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident, Llanelli
OL,14,FTennis and Squash Club said it had
OL,15,Fbeen made aware of the video which was
OL,16,Fposted to Snapchat then uploaded to
OL,17,FFacebook.
