OL,6,FThe club described Mr Barton as a
OL,7,F"valued member of the club" and said
OL,8,Fhe had been visited by representatives
OL,9,Fafter the video came to light.
OL,11,F"He was understandably upset about
OL,12,Fthis incident as he has recently had
OL,13,Ftreatment for cancer," the club said.
OL,15,F"We are a family friendly club and are
OL,16,Fdevastated that our name has been
OL,17,Fbought into this despicable act by a
OL,18,Fperson who has no association with the
OL,19,Fclub and through no fault of our own.
